2f878-13\\nfc_0238072e-a72b-970d-bc68-4e5950b24fc3_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md\",\"offset\":170,\"limit\":120},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"  ok: boolean\\n  skipped?: boolean\\n  error?: string\\n  summary?: Record<string, unknown>\\n}\\n```\\n\\n`EffectPlanResult` / 失败策略见 [16](./16-错误处理与幂等事务.md)。v1：逐条执行，失败默认继续；`critical` 中止。\\n\\n### 8.2 幂等\\n\\n见 [01 §4.1](./01-CallCard数据模型.md)。ledger 存在模拟状态内；重复执行同一出口的同一 effect.id → `skipped: true`。\\n\\n### 8.3 v1 Mock 行为\\n\\n| effect | mock |\\n|--------|------|\\n| `attach_call_card` | **分流**：目标非 voicemail → Profile.Board 增加 pending；目标 voicemail → push VoicemailGenStack（**不写 Board**） |\\n| `unmount_call_card` | 移除/cancelled |\\n| `schedule_call_card` | **分流**：目标非 voicemail → 写入 once intent，到点 `agent_outbound`；目标 voicemail → once intent，到点入栈/物化进信箱（**非**外呼） |\\n| `set_redial_slot` | 更新模拟 `redialSlot` [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":90,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-79d9dbfe-3b2b-4eed-83ea-e4d2de42f878-14\\nfc_0238072e-a72b-970d-bc68-4e5950b24fc3_4\",\"tool_call\":{\"shellToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"command\":\"git diff --stat -- 'docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md' 'docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md' 'docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造_执行索引.md' 2>/dev/null; git log -1 --oneline -- 'docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md' 'docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md' 2>/dev/null; ls -la .ai-workflow-v2-voicemail/prompts/agent-1784787278552.log 2>/dev/null; tail -c 8000 .ai-workflow-v2-voicemail/prompts/agent-1784787278552.log 2>/dev/null | head -c 6000\",\"workingDirectory\":\"\",\"timeout\":30000,\"toolCallId\":\"call-79d9dbfe-3b2b-4eed-83ea-e4d2de42f878-14\\nfc_0238072e-a72b-970d-bc68-4e5950b24fc3_4\",\"simpleCommands\":[\"git\",\"git\",\"ls\",\"tail\",\"head\"],\"hasInputRedirect\":false,\"hasOutputRedirect\":true,\"parsingResult\":{\"parsingFailed\":false,\"e