ed end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":191,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-09b0309a-8d72-40df-8fde-d402fe514155-18\\nfc_1360b8e4-a441-9577-af2e-0e2a737baaf9_0\",\"tool_call\":{\"editToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\",\"streamContent\":\"相关：[02-运行时协议](./02-运行时协议.md) · [11-角色与社交](./11-角色与社交.md) · [07-壳嵌入与导出契约](../技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md) · [语音留言改造需求](../里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造需求.md)\\n\\n## 1. 两层对象\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\",\"linesAdded\":1,\"linesRemoved\":1,\"diffString\":\"--- a//Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\\n+++ b//Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\\n@@ -4,7 +4,7 @@\\n \\n **存档口径**：`CallCardInstance` / `CallCardBoard` 挂在当前用户的 [PlayerProfile](./10-用户与存档.md) 下，不是全局单例。\\n \\n-相关：[02-运行时协议](./02-运行时协议.md) · [11-角色与社交](./11-角色与社交.md) · [07-壳嵌入与导出契约](../技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md)\\n+相关：[02-运行时协议](./02-运行时协议.md) · [11-角色与社交](./11 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":193,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-09b0309a-8d72-40df-8fde-d402fe514155-19\\nfc_1360b8e4-a441-9577-af2e-0e2a737baaf9_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"editToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\",\"streamContent\":\"```ts\\ntype CardKind = \\\"free\\\" | \\\"story\\\" | \\\"system\\\" | \\\"schedule\\\" | \\\"voicemail\\\"\\ntype InteractionMode = \\\"realtime_dialogue\\\" | \\\"playback_only\\\" | \\\"hybrid\\\"\\ntype EntryMode = \\\"inbound_user_dial\\\" | \\\"outbound_auto\\\" | \\\"either\\\" | \\\"mailbox_open\\\"\\n\\ninterface CallCardDefinition {\\n  cardId: string\\n  cardKind: CardKind\\n  title: string\\n  ownerAgentId: string\\n  entryMode: EntryMode\\n  interactionMode: InteractionMode\\n\\n  context: CallCardContext\\n  objectives: CallCardObjectives\\n  toolPolicy: ToolPolicy\\n  assets?: CardAssets\\n\\n  exits: CallCardExit[]\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### 2.1 cardKind\\n\\n| 值 | 含义 |\\n|----|------|\\n| `free` | 自由通话默认卡；每角色应有且仅有一份默认 FreeCallCard（可在角色库配置） |\\n| `story` | 强约束剧情卡 |\\n| `system` |  [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":194,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-09b0309a-8d72-40df-8fde-d402fe514155-20\\nfc_1360b8e4-a441-9577-af2e-0e2a737baaf9_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"editToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\",\"streamContent\":\"| effect | 参数要点 | 语义 |\\n|--------|----------|------|\\n| `attach_call_card` | `agentId`, `cardId`, `activation?` | 见下方 **挂卡分流表**（普通卡 → Board.pending；voicemail → 进信箱生成栈） |\\n| `unmount_call_card` | `agentId`, `cardId?`（缺省卸该角色匹配卡） | 卸卡 |\\n| `schedule_call_card` | `agentId`, `cardId`, `delay: { minMs, maxMs }` | 见下方 **挂卡分流表**（普通卡 → 延迟外呼；voicemail → 延迟进信箱） |\\n| `set_redial_slot` | `agentId`, `cardId?` | 设置重播槽指向该角色（及可选卡） |\\n| ~~`create_voicemail`~~ | — | **已废弃**：校验 error / Schema 拒识；Studio 下拉删除。留言一律用 `cardKind=voicemail` + `attach_call_card` / `schedule_call_card` |\\n| `keep_card_pending` | `cardId?`（默认当前卡） | 通话结束后保持 pending |\"}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-09b0309a-8d72-40df-8fde-d402fe514155-20\\nfc_1360 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":195,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-09b0309a-8d72-40df-8fde-d402fe514155-20\\nfc_1360b8e4-a441-9577-af2e-0e2a737baaf9_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"editToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\",\"streamContent\":\"| effect | 参数要点 | 语义 |\\n|--------|----------|------|\\n| `attach_call_card` | `agentId`, `cardId`, `activation?` | 见下方 **挂卡分流表**（普通卡 → Board.pending；voicemail → 进信箱生成栈） |\\n| `unmount_call_card` | `agentId`, `cardId?`（缺省卸该角色匹配卡） | 卸卡 |\\n| `schedule_call_card` | `agentId`, `cardId`, `delay: { minMs, maxMs }` | 见下方 **挂卡分流表**（普通卡 → 延迟外呼；voicemail → 延迟进信箱） |\\n| `set_redial_slot` | `agentId`, `cardId?` | 设置重播槽指向该角色（及可选卡） |\\n| ~~`create_voicemail`~~ | — | **已废弃**：校验 error / Schema 拒识；Studio 下拉删除。留言一律用 `cardKind=voicemail` + `attach_call_card` / `schedule_call_card` |\\n| `keep_card_pending` | `cardId?`（默认当前卡） | 通话结束后保持 pending |\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":196,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-09b0309a-8d72-40df-8fde-d402fe514155-21\\nfc_1360b8e4-a441-9577-af2e-0e2a737baaf9_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"editToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\",\"streamContent\":\"**不设**独立 `create_relay` / Relay 子系统。旧「带话」语义一律用 `attach_call_card`（或 `schedule_call_card`）+ 目标卡的 `privateBrief` / `speakableBrief` 表达；设计期是否允许引荐见角色 `social.canIntroduce`（[11](./11-角色与社交.md)）。\\n\\n#### 挂卡 / 延迟分流（目标 `cardKind`）\\n\\n| Effect | 目标为普通卡（非 voicemail） | 目标为 `cardKind=voicemail` |\\n|--------|------------------------------|------------------------------|\\n| `attach_call_card` | 写 `Board.pending`（引荐/带话 + 卡上下文） | **不写 Board**；push **VoicemailGenStack**（立即）；plan 终态后物化进信箱 |\\n| `schedule_call_card` | 写 once intent → 到点 `agent_outbound`（外呼响铃） | **不写 Board**；写 once intent，到点 **入栈/物化进信箱**（**不是**外呼响铃） |\\n\\n延迟语义钉死：「N 分钟后信箱多一条留言」，不是「N 分钟后电话响铃播留言卡」。到点若用户正在通话：**仍写入信箱槽**，不打断当前 CallSession。运行时细节见 [02 §8.4–§8.5](./02-运行时协议.md)。\\n [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":197,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-09b0309a-8d72-40df-8fde-d402fe514155-21\\nfc_1360b8e4-a441-9577-af2e-0e2a737baaf9_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"editToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\",\"streamContent\":\"**不设**独立 `create_relay` / Relay 子系统。旧「带话」语义一律用 `attach_call_card`（或 `schedule_call_card`）+ 目标卡的 `privateBrief` / `speakableBrief` 表达；设计期是否允许引荐见角色 `social.canIntroduce`（[11](./11-角色与社交.md)）。\\n\\n#### 挂卡 / 延迟分流（目标 `cardKind`）\\n\\n| Effect | 目标为普通卡（非 voicemail） | 目标为 `cardKind=voicemail` |\\n|--------|------------------------------|------------------------------|\\n| `attach_call_card` | 写 `Board.pending`（引荐/带话 + 卡上下文） | **不写 Board**；push **VoicemailGenStack**（立即）；plan 终态后物化进信箱 |\\n| `schedule_call_card` | 写 once intent → 到点 `agent_outbound`（外呼响铃） | **不写 Board**；写 once intent，到点 **入栈/物化进信箱**（**不是**外呼响铃） |\\n\\n延迟语义钉死：「N 分钟后信箱多一条留言」，不是「N 分钟后电话响铃播留言卡」。到点若用户正在通话：**仍写入信箱槽**，不打断当前 CallSession。运行时细节见 [02 §8.4–§8.5](./02-运行时协议.md)。 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":212,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-7173e470-1b0e-4b0e-8dec-879d7126d57b-22\\nfc_0a7f42bc-2324-9a26-8161-59cab3c276f5_0\",\"tool_call\":{\"updateTodosToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"todos\":[{\"id\":\"vm1-01\",\"content\":\"回写需求 01：CardKind/EntryMode/分流/废弃 create_voicemail\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_COMPLETED\",\"createdAt\":\"1784787326762\",\"updatedAt\":\"1784787373825\",\"dependencies\":[]},{\"id\":\"vm1-02\",\"content\":\"回写需求 02：attach/schedule 分流、物化、听留言 beginCall\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_IN_PROGRESS\",\"createdAt\":\"1784787326762\",\"updatedAt\":\"1784787373825\",\"dependencies\":[]}],\"merge\":true}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-7173e470-1b0e-4b0e-8dec-879d7126d57b-22\\nfc_0a7f42bc-2324-9a26-8161-59cab3c276f5_0\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784787373825\"},\"model_call_id\":\"f5e7fb25-1bbd-4e66-b4fe-9682829ca28d-6-i91m\",\"session_id\":\"bbabb225-f4cb-4520-b3f9-0dcbbd20fe8e\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784787373755}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":214,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-7173e470-1b0e-4b0e-8dec-879d7126d57b-22\\nfc_0a7f42bc-2324-9a26-8161-59cab3c276f5_0\",\"tool_call\":{\"updateTodosToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"todos\":[{\"id\":\"vm1-01\",\"content\":\"回写需求 01：CardKind/EntryMode/分流/废弃 create_voicemail\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_COMPLETED\",\"createdAt\":\"1784787326762\",\"updatedAt\":\"1784787373825\",\"dependencies\":[]},{\"id\":\"vm1-02\",\"content\":\"回写需求 02：attach/schedule 分流、物化、听留言 beginCall\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_IN_PROGRESS\",\"createdAt\":\"1784787326762\",\"updatedAt\":\"1784787373825\",\"dependencies\":[]}],\"merge\":true},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"todos\":[{\"id\":\"vm1-01\",\"content\":\"回写需求 01：CardKind/EntryMode/分流/废弃 create_voicemail\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_COMPLETED\",\"createdAt\":\"1784787326762\",\"updatedAt\":\"1784787373827\",\"dependencies\":[]},{\"id\":\"vm1-02\",\"content\":\"回写需求 02：attach/schedule 分流、物化、听留言 beginCall\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_IN_PROGRESS\",\"createdAt\":\"1784787326762\",\"updatedAt\":\"1784787373827\",\"dependencies\":[]},{\"id\":\"vm1-verify\",\"content\" [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":217,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-7173e470-1b0e-4b0e-8dec-879d7126d57b-23\\nfc_0a7f42bc-2324-9a26-8161-59cab3c276f5_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"editToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md\",\"streamContent\":\"相关：[01](./01-CallCard数据模型.md) · [10](./10-用户与存档.md) · [19](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md) · [50](./50-对话与模型适配.md) · [04](./04-调试器界面需求.md) · [语音留言改造需求](../里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造需求.md)\\n\\n## 1. 主链\\n\\n```text\\n选定 User → 加载 PlayerProfile\\nCallIntent\\n  → CallCardResolver\\n  → 绑定 CallCardInstance；beginCall → CallSession（frozenCard + ComposeScene）\\n  → ContextComposer（只读；promptScenes + 本地时间）\\n  → DialogueAdapter.start(DialogueSessionSpec)\\n  → … DialogueEvent …（工具只登记 RuntimeExitCandidate）\\n  → session.ended + phoneFlags\\n  → Story：OutcomeEvaluator → ExitSelector → EffectExecutor（+ Sink）→ 可选 MemoryCommit\\n  → Free：FreeCallPostPipeline（MemoryCommit → 有候选则 ExitSelector → Effect）\\n  → （若 GenStack 非空）VoicemailMaterializePipeline（plan 终态之后；外置生成 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":218,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-7173e470-1b0e-4b0e-8dec-879d7126d57b-24\\nfc_0a7f42bc-2324-9a26-8161-59cab3c276f5_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"editToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md\",\"streamContent\":\"### 8.3 v1 Mock 行为\\n\\n| effect | mock |\\n|--------|------|\\n| `attach_call_card` | **分流**：目标非 voicemail → Profile.Board 增加 pending；目标 voicemail → push VoicemailGenStack（**不写 Board**） |\\n| `unmount_call_card` | 移除/cancelled |\\n| `schedule_call_card` | **分流**：目标非 voicemail → 写入 once intent，到点 `agent_outbound`；目标 voicemail → once intent，到点入栈/物化进信箱（**非**外呼） |\\n| `set_redial_slot` | 更新模拟 `redialSlot`（可挂 Profile 或会话态） |\\n| ~~`create_voicemail`~~ | **废弃**：校验拒绝；运行时不执行新写。旧 stub 读路径可过渡，不得作为新写真源 |\\n| `keep_card_pending` | 当前 Instance 回到 pending（或保持 pending） |\\n| `set_world_fact` | 更新 Profile.world.facts |\\n| `update_npc_knowledge` | 更新 Profile.world.knowledge（可跨角色） |\\n| `patch_memory` | 更新 Profile.characters[agentId].memory（可跨角色；仅出口阶段 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":219,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-7173e470-1b0e-4b0e-8dec-879d7126d57b-24\\nfc_0a7f42bc-2324-9a26-8161-59cab3c276f5_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"editToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md\",\"streamContent\":\"### 8.3 v1 Mock 行为\\n\\n| effect | mock |\\n|--------|------|\\n| `attach_call_card` | **分流**：目标非 voicemail → Profile.Board 增加 pending；目标 voicemail → push VoicemailGenStack（**不写 Board**） |\\n| `unmount_call_card` | 移除/cancelled |\\n| `schedule_call_card` | **分流**：目标非 voicemail → 写入 once intent，到点 `agent_outbound`；目标 voicemail → once intent，到点入栈/物化进信箱（**非**外呼） |\\n| `set_redial_slot` | 更新模拟 `redialSlot`（可挂 Profile 或会话态） |\\n| ~~`create_voicemail`~~ | **废弃**：校验拒绝；运行时不执行新写。旧 stub 读路径可过渡，不得作为新写真源 |\\n| `keep_card_pending` | 当前 Instance 回到 pending（或保持 pending） |\\n| `set_world_fact` | 更新 Profile.world.facts |\\n| `update_npc_knowledge` | 更新 Profile.world.knowledge（可跨角色） |\\n| `patch_memory` | 更新 Profile.characters[agentId].memory（可跨角色；仅出口 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":237,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-5f648442-d294-4eea-930d-822164ce0bc6-25\\nfc_153e2460-3f73-95c5-8821-098fbcd89e64_0\",\"tool_call\":{\"editToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md\",\"streamContent\":\"在 **当前 Profile** 上：\\n\\n1. `simulate_start`：直接激活指定 `cardId` 的新 Instance（或已有 pending），忽略日常优先级。\\n2. `redial`：若槽指向 `cardId`，优先激活该 Definition 在目标角色上的对应 pending；若无 pending，可按包配置挂卡再激活（校验器应警告「重播未挂卡」）。\\n3. `mailbox_open`：按信箱槽 `voicemailId` + `cardId` 绑定该 **`cardKind=voicemail`** Definition；**不**从 `Board.pending` 挑选；Session 强制 `playback_only` + `entryMode=mailbox_open`。播槽内已物化内容。\\n4. `user_dial` / `agent_outbound`：\\n   - **有效可拨**：`effectiveDialable = !def.isNarrativeOnly && ((def.dialable === true) || (runtime?.unlocked === true))`。\\n   - 若意图为 `user_dial` 且 `!effectiveDialable` → `CHARACTER_NOT_DIALABLE`；`agent_outbound` / `simulate_start` 仍允许（**narrative-only 除外**：外呼亦拒绝，除非调试 force）。\\n   - **禁止**把 `cardKind=voicemail` 解析为待接通剧情卡（voic [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":240,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"cal