llCard数据模型.md\" && grep -q 'mailbox_open' \"docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md\" && grep -q 'create_voicemail' \"docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\" |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":161,"content":"| ✅   | V2-VM-3  | **校验**：voicemail 强制 playback_only+mailbox_open+deny_all；create_voicemail error；VOICEMAIL_* 单测 | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":167,"content":"| ✅   | V2-VM-9  | **Studio Effect**：删除 create_voicemail 面板与枚举；attach/schedule 人话标明进信箱                           | npm run quality:studio                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":168,"content":"| ✅   | V2-VM-10 | **样例包**：`lanxing_voicemail` 改 cardKind；callback 出口 attach 替代 create_voicemail；validate 绿      | npm run quality:engine                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":170,"content":"| ⬜   | V2-VM-12 | **全仓清理**：Sink/旧测试/旧面板文件去掉 create_voicemail 新写路径                                               | npm run quality:engine · npm run quality:studio                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":f