e 增加 mailbox_open；废弃 create_voicemail","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":61,"content":"D Studio：卡种/锁定字段 UI；Effect 下拉去掉 create_voicemail；挂卡可指向留言卡","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":82,"content":"| 细化修改 7 | Effect 面板已有 `create_voicemail` → 本批删除该选项与面板 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":119,"content":"| `create_voicemail` | — | **废弃**：Schema 拒识或 validate error；Studio 下拉删除 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":184,"content":"| Effect 下拉 | **删除** `create_voicemail` 及专属面板 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":201,"content":"| 废弃 effect | `outcome.ts` / Sink 媒介表去掉 `create_voicemail`；旧包 validate 报错并指引改 attach |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":225,"content":"- **历史 `create_voicemail` Sink 分支：** 删除或改为「仅兼容读旧 stub，不新写」——本批推荐 **直接废弃**，样例迁移后无旧路径","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":243,"content":"- [ ] Studio：无 `create_voicemail` 选项；voicemail 卡字段锁定  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":256,"content":"| 需求 01 | CardKind / EntryMode；废弃 create_voicemail；挂卡分流表 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":259,"content":"| 需求 08 | VOICEMAIL_* 校验码（kind/mode 不匹配、create_voicemail 废弃等） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/人类/原始需求讨论记录","matches":[{"lineNumber":89,"content":"再拆 questRuntime.js：Engine / StageRunner / ConditionEvaluator / EffectExecutor。把 call_intent 变成领域 effect：start_call，create_relay，后面还有 create_voicemail、set_world_fact。关键是 effect ledger，避免 replay 后双外呼、双留言。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":465,"content":"      effect: \"create_voicemail\",","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":530,"content":"          effect: \"create_voicemail\",","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI/studio-v2/04-第一幕打错电话-mock拓扑.md","matches":[{"lineNumber"