{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"started","call_id":"call-010de662-39fd-4d0c-a1c0-eb732569c09f-43\nfc_ce9a392c-f38c-9a09-9496-13ac66b6cf6d_3","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md","offset":110,"limit":40}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-010de662-39fd-4d0c-a1c0-eb732569c09f-43\nfc_ce9a392c-f38c-9a09-9496-13ac66b6cf6d_3","startedAtMs":"1784792123395"},"model_call_id":"f12dbec0-e618-4303-97ed-4c0da6d9d7a9-7-l80r","session_id":"7b604dd9-4abf-4259-a8ae-6f931abdf158","timestamp_ms":1784792123392}
[gbx] · 读取 docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-010de662-39fd-4d0c-a1c0-eb732569c09f-43\nfc_ce9a392c-f38c-9a09-9496-13ac66b6cf6d_3","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md","offset":110,"limit":40},"result":{"success":{"content":"      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n另需 `cards/xiaoyu_waiting_user.s-card.json`；仓库样例已落在 `data/storis-packages/golden_handoff/`（含 unlock + attach + redial）。磁盘布局总览见 [19 §3](./19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)。\n\n## 4. Effect 与壳\n\n| Effect | 壳侧（EffectSink） |\n|--------|-------------------|\n| schedule / 外呼类 | 真响铃 / CallIntent |\n| create_voicemail | 真信箱 |\n| set_redial_slot | 重播键（引擎已写 Profile） |\n| set_character_unlocked | **仅引擎写 Profile**；壳无媒介 |\n| play_system_prompt | 系统音 |\n| attach / fact / knowledge / memory / variable | **仅引擎写 Profile**；壳在通话前后调 Host |\n\n时序：Executor 逻辑写盘意图 → Sink 媒介 → plan 终态 → save。详见 [19 §6](./19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)。\n\n包配置与卡文件 **禁止**出现壳内部 API 名、绝对文件路径、handler 函数名。\n\n## 5. 通话中过程事件（DialogueEvent 扩展）\n\n挂机后的 `hangup_early` 出口 ≠ 通话中过程话术。过程事件**不改 Profile**：\n\n| 事件 | 选用 |\n|------|------|\n| `silence_timeout` | `CharacterDef.callFlowPrompts.longSilence` |\n| `call_duration_threshold` | `longCallNudge` |\n| `pre_hangup_hint` | `preHangupFarewell` |\n\n**壳 / DialogueAdapter 负责计时并上报**；引擎只选文案并注入下一轮或请 Adapter 播一句。默认阈值与 Studio 模拟按钮见 [50 §5.4](../需求/50-对话与模型适配.md)；角色可覆盖 `callFlowPolicy`（[11](../需求/11-角色与社交.md)）。\n\n## 6. 版本\n\n- 内容包与 SaveGame 均带 `schemaVersion`\n- 破坏性变更 +1；壳对未知版本应拒绝并提示\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":155,"fileSize":5882,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md","readRange":{"startLine":110,"endLine":149},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-010de662-39fd-4d0c-a1c0-eb732569c09f-43\nfc_ce9a392c-f38c-9a09-9496-13ac66b6cf6d_3","startedAtMs":"1784792123395","completedAtMs":"1784792123563"},"model_call_id":"f12dbec0-e618-4303-97ed-4c0da6