{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-010de662-39fd-4d0c-a1c0-eb732569c09f-44\nfc_ce9a392c-f38c-9a09-9496-13ac66b6cf6d_4","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md","offset":330,"limit":50},"result":{"success":{"content":"- 对 `FREE_PACKAGE_ID` 调用 `loadPackage` / 创建故事目录\n\n**工具：** Free 默认全开 Registry 中 `free` 可用工具（旧话机业务 FC 抽来的七支，见 [13 §7](../需求/13-工具与能力注册.md)）；通话中仍只登记 candidate。\n\n注入：`createEngine({ freeCallPostPipeline })`。Story 卡仍走 Outcome → ExitSelector。存取注入见 [23 §5](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)。\n\n---\n\n## 6. EffectExecutor vs EffectSink\n\n| 组件 | 职责 |\n|------|------|\n| **EffectExecutor** | 引擎内：改 Profile（挂卡、fact、memory、variable、schedule 队列…）+ WET |\n| **EffectSink** | 壳/Studio：媒介副作用（留言、播 WAV、真响铃）；Studio 无硬件时为 mock |\n\n时序：\n\n```text\nExit 选中（或 Free pipeline 发出等价 effect）\n  → Executor 逐条：\n       · 逻辑类：改 Profile + WET\n       · 媒介类：先 WET（intent）→ 调用 EffectSink\n  → plan / pipeline 终态 → completed → save Profile\n```\n\n壳**不得**自己改 Board/Memory；只执行 Sink 与上报 `call.*`。\n\n---\n\n## 7. 动态出口 vs Outcome（求值定稿）\n\n- **Outcome**：挂机后结构化结果（flags、beats…）。\n- **静态 exits**：作者预置 `condition + priority + effects`。\n- **动态 candidates**：通话中工具仅登记；挂机后与静态合并进 ExitSelector。\n\n规则：\n\n1. 候选池 = `frozenCard.exits` ∪ `session.exitCandidates`\n2. 动态带 `exitId` → 使用该静态出口的 condition + effects（candidate 可提高 priority / 提供 hints）\n3. 纯动态必须自带 `effects`；隐式条件 =「candidate 仍有效」AND 基础通话 flags（如 Registry 模板声明须 `answered`）\n4. 同 priority：**静态声明顺序优先于动态**\n\n---\n\n## 8. Resolver 补充定稿\n\n### 8.1 可拨判定（`effectiveDialable`）\n\n```text\neffectiveDialable(def, runtime) =","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":531,"fileSize":22479,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md","readRange":{"startLine":330,"endLine":379},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-010de662-39fd-4d0c-a1c0-eb732569c09f-44\nfc_ce9a392c-f38c-