{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"started","call_id":"call-43775142-7337-4490-a9a8-027c581027c4-91\nfc_2fc4e7ad-efd4-91e4-8bb5-281a0082a62e_2","tool_call":{"editToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/04-调试器界面需求.md","streamContent":"## 6. 电话事件与 Outcome\n\n接通结束、未接、占线、提前挂断、播放完成/跳过、重播、留言已听、回拨触发。预填 flags 后可改 beats，再结束通话。\n\n## 6.1 语音留言信箱（最小调试路径）\n\n与 [语音留言改造需求](../里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造需求.md) §3.5–§3.6、Host 单测对齐；完整调试台大改可后续批。\n\n| 能力 | 口径 |\n|------|------|\n| **信箱列表** | 读 `Profile.telephony.voicemails[]`（真源）；展示 status / text 摘要 / audioRef |\n| **未读** | `deriveVoicemailHasUnread(telephony)`；可观察 `onVoicemailUnreadChanged` 回调（注入桩） |\n| **听完** | 以 `entryMode=mailbox_open` + `cardKind=voicemail` 的 `beginCall` 起会话（`playback_only`）；播完 / 跳过 → Outcome（`voicemail_listened` / `playback_completed` / `playback_skipped`）→ ExitSelector → 该卡 exits |\n| **禁止** | 按普通 `user_dial` / Board.pending 去「拨」留言卡；壳自播完只打 flag、绕过 Session 跑 exits |\n\n## 7. 非目标\n\n- 调试器内改卡或热重载本通 frozenCard\n- v1 强制 Realtime / 自动 Outcome\n- 旧话机进程连接、完整时间旅行（P1）\n"}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-43775142-7337-4490-a9a8-027c581027c4-91\nfc_2fc4e7ad-efd4-91e4-8bb5-281a0082a62e_2","startedAtMs":"1784792261818"},"model_call_id":"f12dbec0-e618-4303-97ed-4c0da6d9d7a9-17-xiak","session_id":"7b604dd9-4abf-4259-a8ae-6f931abdf158","timestamp_ms":1784792261831}
